> According to the spec, you cannot use both. I think this is a reason to
> turn off APM when ACPI is enabled.
On most boards this changes the IRQ pins over to SMI not SMM so its very
much one or the other.
Generally you should favour APM over ACPI nowdays. APM BIOS is buggy as hell
ACPI table errors in todays BIOSen make APM look like heaven
